## 🛠️ KEY FEATURES
- **Voice Generation (TTS):** Integrate with Google TTS (gTTS) to generate realistic voice payloads from custom scripts.
- **Custom Payload Loading:** Load pre-recorded high-fidelity `.wav` or `.mp3` files for more convincing lures.
- **SIP Protocol Support:** Connects directly to the SuperSploit SIP Gateway or any standard commercial VoIP PBX.
- **Live Call Console:** Monitor the SIP handshake in real-time (`INVITE`, `RINGING`, `200 OK`) and track audio transmission status.
- **Caller ID Spoofing:** Leverage your VoIP gateway to present any numeric identity to the target.

